                    <p style="text-align: justify;">
                        One winter, Jen experienced the harsh realities of homelessness firsthand when seven of her
                        friends tragically froze to death due to the unforgiving cold. This devastating loss motivated
                        her to find a solution to help others facing similar struggles. Drawing on her determination
                        and ingenuity, Jen developed high-tech foam vests designed to provide critical warmth even in
                        subzero temperatures. These vests are not only highly effective but also free, making them
                        accessible to those in need. Now no longer homeless herself, Jen is on a mission to ensure that
